channel.title: Project X Fullscreen 317 Development team needed
channel.description:
[size=24pt][b]Project X[/b][/size]
Introduction: Hello my name is james and i am creating a server to run on a 80GB Hard drive and 1GB Ram server. My aim is to create a server with a variety of mini games training zones and skills for people to take part. I would also like to have a variety of skills that can be used.
[size=12pt]Current Working Mini games[/size] Barrows Fight Pits Pest control
[size=12pt]Teleports[/size] Edge Village Varrock (Home) Blue Dragons Ardougne Camelot
[size=12pt]Needed Developers[/size] Spawner this will require using the ::spawn command to spawn npc for the server, creating NPC drops and rates. General moderator this position involves policing the server. Website creator basically to create a fesiable website that looks professional.
[img]http://img12.imageshack.us/img12/2996/bluedragony.png[/img]
Yes i know it say rune mtp i will change that later.
Please post here if you are interest with your email address thanks james
